summary: are you doing commissions with multiple characters allowed? how much would it cost for two characters in a commission?
question: are you doing commissions with multiple characters allowed? how much would it cost for two characters in a commission?
answer:
Hi anon!

Thanks for the question!

I’m currently open for COLOR PENCILS commissions.

The cost of a drawing with 2 characters depends the shot (bust, full body).

COLOR PENCIL / BUST………….. 30€

+ add character……………………….. 15€

COLOR PENCIL / FULL BODY….45€

+add character………………………… 20€

Hope it helps! Thank you so much! :)

summary:
Feijoa with tomatillos
A quick scrawl on cheap Japanese calligraphy paper, not really finished, and the stretchy, soft surface...
body:
Feijoa with tomatillos

A quick scrawl on cheap Japanese calligraphy paper, not really finished, and the stretchy, soft surface is not very receptive to graphite. But the task was oddly more satisfactory than the previous drawing, done with more care and perseverance on lovely cream Lana Dessin 220. Good paper carries expectations in its wonderful fibres, even when it’s reasonably priced like the Lana. Getting past this obstacle is my retirement project.

summary: It ain’t always nice being an artist and having people straight up tell you that the thing you worked so hard to paint/create is...
body:
It ain’t always nice being an artist and having people straight up tell you that the thing you worked so hard to paint/create is just trash or it looks completely unlike what you tried to paint, intentional or not.

But y’know, keep tearing me down. I’m just gonna keep putting my “trash” up everywhere so you have to keep looking at it.
